lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy may need to dial back his aggression and play more "Nicklaus-like" to taste victory at Augusta National, according to former British Open runner-up Thomas Levet.

headline.print_headline: McIlroy Needs to Rein in Aggression to Win Masters: Levet
headline.main: McIlroy Needs to Rein in Aggression to Win Masters: Levet
